Sentencas: The tubular solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) stack has important parameters that need to be identified and optimized for the control of high performance.
Titulo: Parameter optimization for tubular solid oxide fuel cell stack based on the dynamic model and an improved genetic algorithm

Sentencas: In this paper, a simple SOFC electrochemical model which its parameters need to be optimized is introduced to implement stack control for high output power.
Titulo: Parameter optimization for tubular solid oxide fuel cell stack based on the dynamic model and an improved genetic algorithm

Sentencas: A dynamic SOFC model is built based on three sub-models to provide a large numbers simulated data and different condition for optimization.
Titulo: Parameter optimization for tubular solid oxide fuel cell stack based on the dynamic model and an improved genetic algorithm

Sentencas: Unlike the traditional parameter optimization method-simple genetic algorithm (SGA), an improved genetic algorithm (IGA) is introduced.
Titulo: Parameter optimization for tubular solid oxide fuel cell stack based on the dynamic model and an improved genetic algorithm

Sentencas: The proposed method shows more accuracy and validity by comparing the different results using SGA and IGA methods, the simulated data, and experimental data.
Titulo: Parameter optimization for tubular solid oxide fuel cell stack based on the dynamic model and an improved genetic algorithm

Sentencas: The models and IGA method are adapted to control processes.
Titulo: Parameter optimization for tubular solid oxide fuel cell stack based on the dynamic model and an improved genetic algorithm
